    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"appreciating the present\" feels like such a lie when you know the end is coming. if there's no permanence, then there's no point in trying to build anything or feel anything. it's just a cycle of waiting for the inevitable wipe. wouldn't it just be easier to just... accept it? to not fight it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
